42:11.334 --> 42:15.398
♪ NEVER LED ME WRONG,
YOU LED ME RIGHT ♪

42:15.400 --> 42:16.665
♪ LED ME RIGHT ♪

42:16.667 --> 42:20.532
♪ I'MA WALK BY FAITH
